						               													<description>Samachar is a light-strategy card drafting game that was launched at MeepleCon, India 2023.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You take on the role of a Newspaper Publishing company and play against your friends to be the best Newspaper Company in India.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You draft cards and choose to use the same cards as either News Articles or Employees.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All players play simultaneously. Each player has 2 cards in their hands at the start of the game. They collect two cards from the deck. From the 4 cards, they play 1 card and discard 1 card to a discard pile. They then pass the remaining two cards to the player to their left.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can choose to publish various types of News Editions: Daily, Movie, Sports, Regional, World or Current.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when one player publishes 5 News Editions or when 3 News Editions deck run out. Be the first to publish the most number and types of News Editions and win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
